OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain initially. A mix of
OL,7,Fbrighter spells and light showers
OL,8,Freaches all mid-morning. Bright spells
OL,9,Fand a few showers possible through the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fthe odd shower at first, becoming
OL,14,Fcloudier overnight with showers
OL,15,Fbecoming more frequent and heavier at
OL,16,Ftimes. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
