OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith scattered showers, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Becoming dry through the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some bright spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Breezy at times,
OL,10,Fespecially around the Antrim coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,13,FSunday with some brightness. Dry and
OL,14,Fbright start on Monday but turning
OL,15,Fcloudier later. Variable cloud and
OL,16,Fbright spells on Tuesday with some
OL,17,Fshowers, rain later. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
